manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (io.faceotp.faceotp.ActivityMainFlavor) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

playstore_details.title: Face OTP
playstore_details.description:
Face OTP is an AI-based face recognition security service.
Protect personal information and assets(such as cash) with Face OTP

Face OTP is a next-generation AI security service that can be used for authentication after registering your face, instead of email authentication or SMS authentication, which is easy to hack.

You can use Face OTP as an additional authentication step when logging in and (asset of cash, etc.), to protect your personal information and assets safely.

In addition, by providing digital identity authentication and digital ID services, you can authenticate yourself when registering and using global services such as fintech finance and online classes.

When registering Face OTP to the service, a two-step verification code is used, and after registration, the approval process is performed through facial authentication.


We provide total services for businesses as follows

* Provides identity verification (KYC) service when registering as a global member

* Can be used as a filtering method for one account per person

* (Assets such as cash) When transferring, AML and TravelRule services are provided (available from October 2020)

* Notification and event notification service provided (available from October 2020)

* Online class attendance check service (planned)



For other features you need, please contact support@faceotp.org
